Description: Tools for exploring a cleaned package data set built from OECD
    effective labour market exit age data and United Nations World Population
    Prospects demographic indicators. Supports group and country trend plots,
    map-based group comparisons, one-year snapshots, women-versus-men and
    sex-gap analysis, relationship plots, and helper functions that return the
    underlying tidy data.
